{
  "topology_type": "two_stage_ce_cc_full_coupling",
  "description": "Two-Stage CE-CC Amplifier – Full Coupling (Voltage Divider Bias cả 2 tầng). Mạch khuếch đại 2 tầng: tầng 1 CE (Q1, gain cao), tầng 2 CC (Q2, buffer, Rout thấp). Nối tầng qua Cmid. Voltage divider bias (R1a-R2a cho Q1, R1b-R2b cho Q2). Tầng CE có RE1+CE1 bypass. Gain tổng ~ gain CE * 1. BOM: 2 BJT (Q1=2N3904 CE, Q2=2N2222 CC), 7R (R1a=47kΩ 0.25W, R2a=10kΩ 0.25W, RC1=4.7kΩ 0.5W, RE1=1kΩ 0.5W, R1b=47kΩ 0.25W, R2b=10kΩ 0.25W, RE2=1kΩ 0.5W), 4C (CIN=10µF 25V, Cmid=10µF 25V, COUT=10µF 25V, CE1=100µF 16V). VCC=12V.",
